en_182695_0	Election Commission states that certain candidates have been using different gimmicks to win votes in the forthcoming LG elections.
en_182695_1	Commission Chairman, Mahinda Deshapriya has advised voters that they should not fall prey to such manipulations.
en_182695_2	He said there have been reports of certain voters receiving funds to travel overseas for employment.
en_182695_3	The Election Commission asks voters to inform the commission via 1919 of such incidents.
